		"description": "<h3><strong>Optional Prerequisites</strong></h3><p>To multiclass into the lancer motif class, a character must meet both of the following prerequisites:</p><ul><li><p>Strength 13 or higher</p></li><li><p>Wisdom 13 or higher</p><p></p></li></ul><h3><strong>Multiclassing Proficiencies</strong></h3><p>Multiclassing into lancer grants the following proficiencies: medium armor, shields, and lances.</p><p></p><h3><strong>Multiclassing into Adept</strong></h3><p>If you multiclass into adept, you may add together your lancer and adept levels for the purposes of determining how much extra exertion you gain as an adept.</p><p></p><h3><strong>Multiclassing into Fighter</strong></h3><p>If you multiclass into fighter you may add your lancer and fighter levels together to determine how many combat traditions and maneuvers you gain.&nbsp;</p>",
